Package: libbitc-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libbitc (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for libbitc.
 This package contains headers for libbitc, a C library that allows for bitcoin operations and connection to the bitcoin network.

